            <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:.85rem;color:#1e3a5f;">Multi-Tenant Orgs</div>
                <div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-muted);">Organizations with workspaces, role-based access control, and subscription management.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:.65rem;align-items:flex-start;">
