        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:.65rem;align-items:flex-start;">
            <div class="stat-icon" style="background:rgba(14,165,233,.1);color:#38bdf8;flex-shrink:0;width:34px;height:34px;font-size:.85rem;"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill"></i></div>
            <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:.85rem;color:#1e3a5f;">Super Admin</div>
                <div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-muted);">Centralized admin console for orgs, revenue, SEO, AI config, docs, and blog management.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:.65rem;align-items:flex-start;">
            <div class="stat-icon" style="background:rgba(168,85,247,.1);color:#a855f7;flex-shrink:0;width:34px;height:34px;font-size:.85rem;"><i class="bi bi-search"></i></div>
